{"TopicId":216082,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"No Kerbal Ragdolls","CreatedByName":"BowlerHatGuy3","CreatedById":222738,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T00:10:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BowlerHatGuy3","CreatedById":222738,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T00:10:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaven\u2019t seen anyone talk about this. Kerbal ragdolling was half the fun of Kerbal 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-31T19:32:15Z\u0022 title=\u002203/31/2023 07:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 31, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by BowlerHatGuy3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EGot rid of request for mods\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T00:35:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could not disagree more. Watching a Kerbal slide down a slope on Minmus for 15 minutes, unable to even switch control to something else so I can at least be productive while they slide, was a terrible \u0022feature\u0022 that I\u0027m happy to know is not in KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf all you want is them to fall down sometimes, sure that\u0027s fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T02:25:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216082\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680221424\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222738\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BowlerHatGuy3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, BowlerHatGuy3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Mods can you move this to dev suggestions)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T02:31:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267550\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216082\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680229503\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember: just because you can, doesn\u0027t mean you should.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T19:27:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267529\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216082\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680222903\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could not disagree more. Watching a Kerbal slide down a slope on Minmus for 15 minutes, unable to even switch control to something else so I can at least be productive while they slide, was a terrible \u0022feature\u0022 that I\u0027m happy to know is not in KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf all you want is them to fall down sometimes, sure that\u0027s fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCouldn\u2019t disagree moar. The rag dolls where a very important part of the \u2018kerbalness\u2019 of KSP. It\u2019s hugely important. The fact it isn\u2019t in KSP 2 is very likely to do with the barebones EA release.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-24T04:23:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease bring this back, it was so funny watching Kerbals just tumble around like that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaypeg","CreatedById":228190,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-24T04:26:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think its important and should be added, but also have a \u0022hard-cancel\u0022 feature where if you tap space, it just immediately cancels the ragdoll\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}